#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.dt.day_name.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.dt.day_name"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:1
msgid "Return the day names with specified locale."
msgstr "返回指定语言环境下的星期名称。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:3
msgid ""
"Locale determining the language in which to return the day name. Default "
"is English locale (``'en_US.utf8'``). Use the command ``locale -a`` on "
"your terminal on Unix systems to find your locale language code."
msgstr ""
"决定返回星期名称所用语言的区域设置。默认为英语区域设置（``'en_US.utf8'``"
"）。在 Unix 系统上，可以使用命令 ``locale -a`` 在终端中查找你的区域语言"
"代码。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:9
msgid "Series or Index of day names."
msgstr "包含星期名称的 Series 或 Index。"

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:13
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of
#: pandas.core.accessor.PandasDelegate._add_delegate_accessors.<locals>._create_delegator_method.<locals>.f:34
msgid ""
"Using the ``locale`` parameter you can set a different locale language, "
"for example: ``idx.day_name(locale='pt_BR.utf8')`` will return day names "
"in Brazilian Portuguese language."
msgstr ""
"通过使用 ``locale`` 参数可以设置不同的语言环境，例如：``idx.day_name("
"locale='pt_BR.utf8')`` 将返回巴西葡萄牙语的星期名称。"

